iA few days ago, I used the Leaflet JavaScript module for a project		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ithat required maps. However, when searching for map data sources, I		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ifound that Amap's satellite imagery cannot be zoomed to high precision		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ioutside mainland China, showing no satellite imagery for that area;		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
