iAfter some research, I discovered that Amap's satellite imagery		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iconsists of two layers: the satellite layer and the street layer.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iMoreover, both Amap and Google China maps use China's "Mars Coordinate		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iSystem" encryption, meaning their maps can be directly overlaid		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iwithout misalignment. By combining Amap's street layer with Google		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
iChina's satellite layer, we obtain an electronic map that supports		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
ihigh-precision zooming while displaying street information.		{{server_host}}	{{server_port}}
